personalInfo.residence: Ashville, North Carolina and Jupiter, Florida

tourBios.carHigh:
2015: Joined PGA TOUR Latinoamérica with a solo ninth finish at the Peru Q-School in January... Had one top-10, three top-25s and 10 cuts made in 16 starts on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica. Best finish was T4 at the Hyundai-BBVA Abierto de Chile, where he carded a 64 on the final round in October. Finished the year ranked 64th on the Order of Merit.

Finished T21 at the 84th Abierto OSDE del Centro in April and at the Dominican Republic Open in June for two top-25s in eight starts during the first half of the Latin American season.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Latinoameri was T4th in 2015 at the Hyundai-BBVA 89 Abierto de Chile.
